1. At installatio location of 1.5bbeta4, from command line type: .\build.bat 
squiggle
2. Squiggle loads, select File:Open File

EXPECTED:
No error dialog loads

ACTUAL:
Java.exe - no disk error dialog loads.  Contains the following:
There is no disk in the drive. Please insert a disk into drive \Device\Harddisk2

There are Cancel, Try Again and Continue buttons.

SVG file to open can continue.
